title: Dirt Devil 360° Reach: Power and versatility in the palm of your hand.
description:
Vac, dust & reach — versatility to clean where your upright vac can’t. 360° Reach™ speeds through messes from floor to ceiling with Vac+Dust Tools with SWIPES™. 

Snap on the Crevice Tool and extend your cleaning reach to get the small stuff—high and low.

asset.author: Dirt Devil
asset.hookText:
Vac, dust & reach — versatility to clean where your upright vac can’t. 360° Reach™ speeds through messes from floor to ceiling with Vac+Dust Tools with SWIPES™. 

Snap on the Crevice Tool and extend your cleaning reach to get the small stuff—high and low. Then clean every part of each step with the Powered Stair & Upholstery Tool. When you’re through, dump the dirt with the touch of a button.
